				<wikidot:authorName>Gaffsey</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6590029</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I actually thought that the eggs saying sad stuff was by far the weakest part of the article. However, the image of <em>an</em> Anderson becoming a religious maniac who makes robot animals touches on a lot of things that are of personal interest for me (the intersection of American folk art and religion, the rise of evangelical Christian sects in the late 19th century), so this is actually a pretty easy +1 from me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
